name: MagnetStreet
tag_list: real-estate, marketing, weddings, ecommerce, printing, wedding-invitations, calendars, magnets, save-the-date
overview: MagnetStreet provides custom printing and stationery through its website http://www.magnetstreet.com. Founded in 1995, the company originally served the Real Estate industry exclusively, providing full color calendar magnets. They continue to offer marketing solutions for agents today but more and more customers have turned to MagnetStreet for custom printing including colleges and universities, pro sports teams and brides-to-be. In addition to promotional products for business, MagnetStreet offers a full line of wedding and personal stationery. They are best known for their save the date magnets, sent by brides so their guests can reserve their upcoming wedding date. MagnetStreet is the winner of several industry awards and has been featured in The Washington Post, Brides Magazine and REALTOR Magazine. Headquartered in Chicago, IL, the company has 3 locations and ships product across North America.
